Interface Fn2<A,B,C>

  • Type Parameters:

    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface Fn2<A,B,C>
extends Fn1<A,Fn1<B,C>>
    A function taking two arguments. Note that defining Fn2 in terms of Fn1 provides a reasonable approximation of currying in the form of multiple apply overloads that take different numbers of arguments.
    See Also:
    Fn1
